        "description": "If the currently fetching connection requires any interactive credentials for fetching, Salt Edge will send the [Interactive callback](#interactive). Make sure to specify the `Interactive URL` in your client account by accessing <a href='https://www.saltedge.com/clients/callbacks/edit' target=\"_blank\">callbacks page</a>.\n\nUpon receiving the interactive callback, your app should ask the user for the interactive credentials and send them to the `/interactive` route for the connection. After that, the fetching process will continue as usual.\n",
