        "summary": "Reconnect a connection",
        "description": "In order to [reconnect](#connections-reconnect) a connection, your app needs to send the credentials object, connection's `id`, [consent object](#consents-object) and/or [attempt object](#attempts-object). This means that the consent confirmation should be handled on the client's side, and the 'access terms' the customer agreed on should be passed.\n",
